## âœ… Sample REST API Endpoint (Manual Docs Style)

### POST /api/users
- **Purpose:** Create a new user
- **Request:**
```json
{
  "name": "Ajay",
  "email": "ajay@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}
```
- **Response:**
```json
{
  "message": "User created",
  "user": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Ajay"
  }
}
```

### GET /api/users
- **Purpose:** Get all users
- **Returns:** List of users

